{
  "stem": "26276.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They started to cry like children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took out from their pockets cigarettes, packs of chocolate, whatever they had to give us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then when we start making louder noises-- whistling, dancing, running around all over like a celebration-- then a lot of our prisoners-- the guards must've been afraid to come down from over there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they must have known the night before already that something's going to happen that morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of them were dressed up like we were, in the blue stripe uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what we had was our hair on our heads was shaved in a cross-- two inches going this way and two inches going this way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in case you wanted to escape, somebody's going to recognize you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the hats that we had to wear that were like berets, you couldn't cover it up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You understand what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You still would see those four clumps of hair hanging down at you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't get hair cuts, except this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when we saw those guys in those boots, everybody who was able to walk a little bit or to run a little bit-- I remember just like now-- it was right near the main entrance on the left hand side.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ripped off a machine gun from one of the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you didn't have to rip them off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you just went to it that you didn't know how to ask him for it but they just took it off and they gave it to you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I climbed up at that booth and I must've put-- I emptied the magazine-- I don't know how many bullets were in it-- into one storm trooper.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
